Guidelines to run simulations using the Vensim Version.

1.- Download Vensim Model Reader: https://vensim.com/free-downloads/

2.- Open Policy.xlsx file

	- Modify policy intensities for the case study that you are thinking of simulating.
	- Save the file with the applied changes.

3.- Open "RethinkAction_CS_model.mdl" with Vensim Model Reader

	- Select a name for your policy action scenario.
	- Run the simulation.
	- Visualise the results by selecting an plotting each variable.
	- You can check the "Vensim_buttons_location.jpg" to find help to run the simulation with the previous steps.
